node.title: Most successful people in business do this.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Jason Capital on September 10, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, standing, tree and outdoors.

node.text:
TRY THIS EXERCISE: This is called the “Bow”. It’s a breathing exercise. Opens you right up. Works great. And looks weird too! When we were done, this student said, “I feel so light”. How many of us spend our days feeling like things are so heavy? What if I told you it doesn’t have to be? Understand: The world can’t make things heavy on you. You have to take what the world is giving you and make it heavy first. In this way, you are response-able. In our minds, there are really only two things we can control: our interpretations and our responses. And it’s that little space between WHAT HAPPENED and our interpretation of it where possibility lives. If you let others fill that space for you with THEIR interpretation, you’re likely to end up carrying out THEIR response. In other words, be your own guru. Make your own meaning. Outside of the laws of physics, everything is negotiable. 

P.S. Do you like to travel? My team and I are looking for a few more ppl who want to earn a full-time passive income from home using AirBNB without owning property. If you’re interested, message me the word “Travel”. Thanks!
